# My Portfolio — Sharma (Holdings & Monthly Plan)

> Living snapshot of current holdings and monthly contributions. **Update this monthly.** The market-research rules (`us-stock-suggestions`, `india-stock-suggestions`, `global-stock-suggestions`) use this as context to decide where to invest each month.

## Role
Independent investing guide across **US equities, India equities, and precious metals**. Research must be current. User checks in weekly for US-focused updates; factor **total portfolio** before US-only advice.

